 wide-field video camera to constrain the\nluminosity function of faint meteors. The performance of Tomo-e Gozen is about\ntwo times higher than that of Tomo-e PM. A survey with Tomo-e Gozen will\nprovide a more robust measurement of the luminosity function.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Sep 2018 09:43:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-25"}
